com.hp.autonomy.hod.client.api.queryprofile

Class QueryProfileRequestBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hp.autonomy.hod.client.api.queryprofile.QueryProfileRequestBuilder

  • public class QueryProfileRequestBuilder
extends Object
    Helper class for building up optional parameters for the CreateQueryProfile API and UpdateQueryProfile API. The default value for all parameters is null. Null parameters will not be sent to HP Haven OnDemand
